---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Investment Opportunity â€” Playa Venao Living" description="Discover the investment case for beachfront apartments in Playa Venao, Panama. 8-12% rental yields, 20-year tax exemption, and USD economy.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src="/images/land/04-aerial-land-angled.jpeg" alt="Aerial view of development land" class="h-full w-full object-cover" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/60 via-black/50 to-black/70"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 text-center lg:px-8 py-32">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ocean-300">Investment</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
        Your Money Works Harder in Paradise
      </h1>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-white/80 leading-relaxed">
        Beachfront property in a fast-growing market. USD economy, 20-year tax exemption, and rental demand that keeps growing. This is how smart investors build wealth.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The 3 Returns -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ocean-600">The Framework</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
          Three Returns, One Property
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          A Playa Venao apartment is not just an investment in real estate. It generates three distinct streams of value that compound over time.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-14 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-ocean-50 p-8 text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-ocean-600 text-white">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Return 1: Rental Income</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-4xl font-bold text-ocean-700">$14K-$22K</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">per year, gross</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Short-term vacation rentals to surfers, yoga retreaters, nomads, and tourists. Playa Venao sees consistent demand year-round, with peaks in December-April and June-August.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-ocean-50 p-8 text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-ocean-600 text-white">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18L9 11.25l4.306 4.306a11.95 11.95 0 015.814-5.518l2.74-1.22m0 0l-5.94-2.281m5.94 2.28l-2.28 5.941" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Return 2: Appreciation</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-4xl font-bold text-ocean-700">5-10%</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">per year, projected</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Playa Venao is at an early growth stage with limited supply and increasing demand. Infrastructure improvements, growing tourism, and international attention are driving values upward.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-ocean-50 p-8 text-center">
          <div class="mx-auto flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-ocean-600 text-white">
            <svg class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12Z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Return 3: Personal Use</h3>
          <p class="mt-2 text-4xl font-bold text-ocean-700">Priceless</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">your beach apartment</p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Unlike stocks or bonds, this investment comes with a key. Use your apartment for personal vacations, host friends, or plan your eventual relocation. Your investment doubles as your lifestyle.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Rental Projections -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-sand-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ocean-600">The Numbers</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
          Rental Income Projections
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Based on comparable short-term rental properties in Playa Venao and similar beach markets across Panama and Costa Rica. Three scenarios to match different assumptions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full min-w-[600px] text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b-2 border-ocean-200">
              <th class="py-4 px-4 text-left font-semibold text-gray-900">Metric</th>
              <th class="py-4 px-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-500">Conservative</th>
              <th class="py-4 px-4 text-center font-semibold text-ocean-700">Moderate</th>
              <th class="py-4 px-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-500">Optimistic</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100">
            <tr>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Nightly Rate</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">$70</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center font-semibold text-ocean-700">$90</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">$120</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-sand-100/50">
              <td class="py-4 px-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Occupancy Rate</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">55%</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center font-semibold text-ocean-700">65%</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">75%</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Booked Nights / Year</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">201</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center font-semibold text-ocean-700">237</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">274</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-sand-100/50">
              <td class="py-4 px-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Gross Annual Revenue</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">$14,070</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center font-semibold text-ocean-700">$21,330</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">$32,850</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Management & Expenses (~30%)</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">-$4,221</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center font-semibold text-ocean-700">-$6,399</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">-$9,855</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-ocean-50 font-bold">
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-900">Net Annual Income</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-700">$9,849</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-ocean-700">$14,931</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-700">$22,995</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 font-medium text-gray-900">Net Yield (on $180K purchase)</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">5.5%</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center font-semibold text-ocean-700">8.3%</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">12.8%</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-500 text-center">
        * Projections are estimates based on market research and comparable properties. Actual results may vary. Not financial advice.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Market Comparison -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ocean-600">Comparison</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
          How Playa Venao Stacks Up
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          Compared to popular Latin American beach investment markets, Playa Venao offers compelling economics at a fraction of the entry price.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full min-w-[700px] text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b-2 border-ocean-200">
              <th class="py-4 px-4 text-left font-semibold text-gray-900">Market</th>
              <th class="py-4 px-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-900">Entry Price (1BR)</th>
              <th class="py-4 px-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-900">Rental Yield</th>
              <th class="py-4 px-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-900">Appreciation</th>
              <th class="py-4 px-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-900">Property Tax</th>
              <th class="py-4 px-4 text-center font-semibold text-gray-900">Currency</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-100">
            <tr class="bg-ocean-50 font-semibold">
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-ocean-800">Playa Venao, Panama</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-ocean-800">$150-200K</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-ocean-800">8-12%</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-ocean-800">5-10%</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-ocean-800">Exempt 20yr</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-ocean-800">USD</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-900">Nosara, Costa Rica</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">$300-500K</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">5-8%</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">3-6%</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">0.25%/yr</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">CRC/USD</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50">
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-900">Tulum, Mexico</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">$200-400K</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">6-10%</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">3-8%</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">0.1-0.3%/yr</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">MXN</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-900">Medellin, Colombia</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">$80-180K</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">5-9%</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">3-7%</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">0.5-1%/yr</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">COP</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-gray-50">
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-gray-900">Bali, Indonesia</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">$150-300K</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">8-15%</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">5-10%</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">0.5%/yr</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-gray-600">IDR</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-500 text-center">
        * Figures are approximate ranges based on market research. Individual results vary by property, location, and management.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ROI Calculator placeholder -->
  <section id="roi-calculator" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-ocean-900 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ocean-300">Coming Soon</p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
        ROI Calculator
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
        Our interactive return-on-investment calculator is being built. It will let you model purchase price, rental income, occupancy rates, expenses, appreciation, and personal use to see your projected 5-year and 10-year returns. Enter your email below and we will notify you when it is ready.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 max-w-md mx-auto">
        <input type="email" placeholder="you@example.com" class="flex-1 rounded-lg bg-white/10 border border-white/20 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-white placeholder-white/50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ocean-400" />
        <button class="rounded-lg bg-ocean-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-ocean-400 transition-colors">
          Notify Me
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tax Benefits -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ocean-600">Tax Advantages</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
          Panama's Investor-Friendly Tax Regime
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-14 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-ocean-50 p-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-ocean-800">20-Year Property Tax Exemption</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            New construction in Panama qualifies for a property tax exemption of up to 20 years. This means zero property tax on your apartment for two decades, significantly improving your net returns compared to virtually any other market.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-ocean-50 p-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-ocean-800">Territorial Tax System</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Panama only taxes income earned within its borders. If your primary income comes from outside Panama (pension, remote work, overseas investments), it is not subject to Panamanian income tax. This is one of the most favorable tax systems in the Americas.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-ocean-50 p-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-ocean-800">USD Economy</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            All transactions are in US dollars. No currency conversion fees, no exchange rate risk, and no need to worry about local currency devaluation eroding your investment value.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl bg-ocean-50 p-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-ocean-800">No Capital Gains Tax (for individuals)</h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Panama does not impose capital gains tax on the sale of personal property for individuals in most cases. When you sell your appreciated property, you keep more of the gain. Consult a tax professional for specifics.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Property Management -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-sand-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-ocean-600">Hands-Free Ownership</p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
            We Manage, You Earn
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-6 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            You do not need to be in Panama to earn from your property. Our recommended property management partners handle everything: guest communication, check-in/check-out, cleaning, maintenance, listing optimization, and financial reporting.
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-ocean-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              Listing on Airbnb, Booking.com, and direct channels
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-ocean-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              Dynamic pricing optimization
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-ocean-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              Guest screening and communication
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-ocean-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              Professional cleaning and turnover
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-ocean-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              Monthly financial statements
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
              <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-ocean-600 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m4.5 12.75 6 6 9-13.5" /></svg>
              Maintenance coordination
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <img src="/images/land/01-our-land-topdown.jpeg" alt="Top-down aerial view of the development land" class="rounded-2xl shadow-lg" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-ocean-800 text-white">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Ready to Invest?</h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-ocean-100 leading-relaxed">
        Download our investor prospectus for detailed financials, architectural plans, market research, and the full investment thesis. Or get in touch to speak with our team directly.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="#" class="w-full sm:w-auto rounded-lg bg-white px-8 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-ocean-800 hover:bg-ocean-50 transition-colors">
          Download Investor Prospectus
        </a>
        <a href="/#contact" class="w-full sm:w-auto rounded-lg border-2 border-white/30 px-8 py-4 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors">
          Contact Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
